<item>
            <title>[LU-19062] layout pattern printing is poorly implemented</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19062</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;layout2name()&lt;/tt&gt; function that prints the LOV patterns is implemented poorly, checking all of the individual pattern flag combinations, rather than checking the individual bits and printing them in a list.  It should be reimplemented to handle arbitrary combinations of pattern flags.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
